subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Anna Chakvetadze won her second consecutive tournament, making quick work of the surprise finalist Sania Mirza, 6-3, 6-2, yesterday to win the Bank of the West Classic in Stanford, Calif. Chakvetadze improved to 6-0 in finals and will rise to No. 6 in the world rankings.
